ory and human experience are best preserved in writing The California State Library believes deeply in equity and that libraries are fundamental in empowering people to take charge of their lives their governments and their communities With the growing awareness of our diversity libraries provide wonderful places for us to learn of the rich traditions and cultures that come together in our communities The library collections we build the access we provide and the technologies we embrace will carry the people of California into a productive and creative future The staff of the California State Library believes deeply in the future of California and that libraries have an essential role to play in that future html starrcv cfm Biographical Information on the State Librarian Please send comments and suggestions to mailto csl adm library ca gov csl adm library ca gov State Library Adminstration Office 916 654 0183 Last Updated October 20 2003 PageTop Back to Top of Page conditions cfm Conditions of Use privacy cfm Privacy Policy content Comments comments cfm E mail Webmaster 2003 State of California The content found herein may not necessarily represent the views and opinions of the Schwarzenegger Administration 
